#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- Assigned user will confirm the Repair, start the repair, finish the "
"repairing work and inform the Helpdesk user for the same through Chatter "
"functionality."
msgstr ""
"Den tildelte bruger bekræfter reparationen, påbegynder og afslutter arbejdet "
"og giver herefter kundeservicemedarbejderen besked via chatterfunktionen."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- Customer can <font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\"><strong>raise a "
"ticket</strong></font> to Customer Care team for Repair through mail, "
"\"Submit a Ticket\" form or clicking on Chat bot button in Help page in "
"Website. Support\n"
"            Ticket will be generated in Helpdesk app."
msgstr ""
"- Kunder kan <font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\"><strong>indsende en "
"supportanmodning</strong></font> vedrørende reparation via e-mail til "
"kundeserviceteamet, via formularen »Indsend en supportanmodning« eller ved "
"at klikke på chatbot-knappen på hjemmesidens hjælpeside. Supportsager\n"
"            oprettes i Kundeserviceappen."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- Helpdesk User will create Repair in draft mode and fills up Customer's "
"details in it like equipment to be repaired, warranty end date, etc."
msgstr ""
"- Kundeservicemedarbejderen opretter en reparationsopgave i udkasttilstand "
"og udfylder kundeoplysninger som f.eks. det apparat, der skal repareres, og "
"garantiens udløbsdato."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- Helpdesk user will confirm with the customer whether they will pick up the "
"equipment from repairing site or request to deliver the equipment to their "
"address."
msgstr ""
"- Kundeservicemedarbejderen aftaler med kunden, om enheden skal afhentes på "
"værkstedet, eller om den skal leveres til kundens adresse."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- In case of delivery to customer's address, Helpdesk user will communicate "
"with the customer after delivery and take confirmation from customer about "
"equipment working and\n"
"            <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\">closes the "
"Ticket</font></strong><font style=\"color: rgb(181, 214, 165);\">.</font>"
msgstr ""
"- Ved levering til kundens adresse følger kundeservicemedarbejderen op efter "
"leveringen, får kunden til at bekræfte, at anlægget fungerer, og\n"
"            <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\">lukker "
"herefter sagen</font></strong><font style=\"color: rgb(181, 214, 165);\">.</"
"font>"

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- In case of pick up, ticket will be closed after customer's confirmation of "
"checking equipment at repairing site."
msgstr ""
"- Ved afhentning lukkes sagsnummeret, når kunden har bekræftet, at udstyret "
"er blevet gennemgået på værkstedet."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"- Inventory user <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\">will "
"validate</font></strong> returned equipment in Return and check the <font "
"style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\"><strong>warranty end date</strong></"
"font>. If the\n"
"            warranty date is not under the warranty period, an invoice will "
"be raised for the parts replaced and repairing charge."
msgstr ""
"- Lagermedarbejderen <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\">"
"godkender</font></strong> det returnerede udstyr i \"Retur\" og kontrollerer "
"<font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\"><strong>garantiens udløbsdato</"
"strong></font>. Hvis\n"
"            udstyret ikke er dækket af garanti, udstedes der en faktura for "
"de udskiftede dele og reparationsomkostningerne."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid "- Warranty end date is fetched from delivery of the equipment."
msgstr "- Garantiens udløbsdato fastsættes ved levering af anlægget."

