msgid ""
"Assignees fill up the Worksheet after completion of the Installation. "
"Several <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\">images of Solar "
"System installation</font></strong> of Client's site are captured along with "
"the\n"
"            customer's confirmation and signature in Worksheet. The "
"worksheet includes customized fields like Start date, End date, plan, "
"signature, etc which are configured through\n"
"            <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(165, 74, 123);\">Studio App</"
"font></strong>."
msgstr ""
"De udpegede personer udfylder arbejdsarket, når installationen er afsluttet. "
"Der registreres flere <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);\">"
"billeder af installationen af solcelleanlægget</font></strong> hos kunden "
"sammen med\n"
"            kundens bekræftelse og underskrift på arbejdsarket. Arbejdsarket "
"indeholder brugerdefinerede felter såsom startdato, slutdato, plan og "
"underskrift, som konfigureres via\n"
"            <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(165, 74, 123);\">Studio-appen</"
"font></strong>."

