#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Sales Person is assigned and <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74);"
"\">Opportunity is moved</font></strong> <strong><font style=\"color: "
"rgb(107, 165, 74);\">to Qualified stage</font></strong>. Sales Person "
"follows up with\n"
"            customers through Activities like Calls, Meetings, etc. If the "
"customer agrees the quotation, a site survey is planned and Opportunity is "
"moved to the Site Survey stage."
msgstr ""
"Salgsmedarbejderen tildeles og <strong><font style=\"color: rgb(107, 165, 74)"
";\">salgsmuligheden flyttes</font></strong> <strong><font style=\"color: rgb"
"(107, 165, 74);\"> til fasen \"Kvalificeret\"</font></strong>. "
"Salgsmedarbejderen følger op med\n"
"            kunderne gennem aktiviteter som opkald, møder osv. Hvis kunden "
"accepterer tilbuddet, planlægges en besigtigelse, og salgsmuligheden flyttes "
"til fasen \"Besigtigelse\"."

#. module: solar_installation
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:solar_installation.homepage
